{"tid":1984172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［鬥黃台］OK 你真係忍唔住要批鬥同路人嘅 麻煩你入呢個po","createTime":"2020-04-22T09:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T16:08:49.000Z","uid":75796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9914ea707e6c8ce791c447d71683e9f5837fb8c1","tid":1984172,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位巴絲 <br />\n<br />\n假若你今日個fd去咗食m記，達哥又開台，聽到有人番工搭黨鐵都好。你好唔gur，好失望，一肚氣，就算點勸佢佢都有佢嘅理由令你接受唔到。<br />\n<br />\n所以你想喺連登講，睇下道理喺唔喺自己度嘅話，fine，我明白你嘅心情。<span style=\"color: red;\">但唔該你唔好開po講，更加唔好推到上熱門，因為鬥黃係唔會令我地贏。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">但我真係好想講岀嚟喎</span><br />\n好，咁不如我開個po俾你地留言慢慢講<br />\n當然最好係開喺成人台，因為成人台開po好似上唔到熱門，但咁樣會影響到成人台，所以暫時我只係諗到呢個方法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得咁做ok嘅話，可以試下貼呢個po嘅link去鬥黃嘅post再用不推文防止佢地推上熱門。<br />\n<br />\n咁做仲有一個好處，睇得岀邊幾個user係專做分化同玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有其他建議歡迎提供<br />\n<br />\n最後希望連登仔唔好再鬥黃，多啲喺屋企強身健體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKSTg1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKSTg1p.jpg&h=5e46221d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbca450b127a5ae2e2395e404326425a6dc5325b","tid":1984172,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"c95c7edf099cf6ef21195212354c652954194bf7","tid":1984172,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"再推多下"},{"pid":"0b973a7d306904c0a0ceab44eb6d7916e8477480","tid":1984172,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"cba2d8ad17faf8720aaeb3954021e2a4267b4fbe","tid":1984172,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"慢慢推"},{"pid":"864a78667a2e12a645b55f2736834c2b8627e635","tid":1984172,"uid":68496